title: FYP #25 Committed
description:
When you choose to live fully known by others in deep community, there will come a point where you will run into conflict. We don’t need to fear it. We need to lean into conflict and be people who work through it and stay.

Download the book club PDF: jennieallen.com

Get a copy of Find Your People: findyourpeoplebook.com
